Source: Otago Witness
Author:
Vol / Page: 5
Edition:
Quote: And Jock, my man, when ye hae weans, / Ne'er fash wi' edication, / But pack them aff to herd the kye, / Or to some shepherd's station: / An' see that ye get a' they win, / An' bring them up wi' rigour; / Ne'er fash your thume, although your bairns / Be hasthered like a nigger.
